ll-3580744">Boardmasters</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/victorious-festival-announces-headliners-for-2024-buy-tickets-3553549">Victorious Festival 活动</a>。</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/courteeners-english-teacher-louis-tomlinson-honoured-at-first-ever-northern-music-awards-3750149">该乐队在四月份的首届北方音乐奖上被评为年度乐队</a>。</p><p>去年九月，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/courteeners-the-libertiens-club-nme-ladbrokes-live-3499586">Courteeners 在伦敦举办了一场喧闹的演出，以纪念 Club NME 的重新推出</a>。演出结束后<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-libertines">，The Libertines</a>的 Carl Barât 和 Gary Powell 带来了令人惊喜的 DJ 表演。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/courteeners-announce-intimate-warm-up-show-ahead-of-uk-festival-dates-buy-tickets-3762190">Courteeners 宣布在英国音乐节日期之前进行亲密热身表演的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
