y-corgan-taylor-swift@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billy-corgan-taylor-swift@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billy-corgan-taylor-swift@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billy-corgan-taylor-swift@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smashing-pumpkins">粉碎的南瓜的比利·科根</a>（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billy-corgan">Billy Corgan）</a>赞扬了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>（Taylor Swift），并捍卫了她的最新专辑《折磨诗人部》（The Torred Poets Department）的长度 - 看看他对下面的流行歌星有何看法。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/the-smashing-pumpkins-atum-review-3438260">粉碎的南瓜 - “ atum”评论：带有国歌的轰炸太空摇滚歌剧</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>科根（Corgan） <a href="https://www.irishtimes.com/culture/music/2024/06/03/smashing-pumpkins-billy-corgan-taylor-swift-is-one-of-the-most-gifted-pop-artists-of-all-time-how-is-it-a-bad-thing-that-shes-releasing-more-music/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在谈到《<em>爱尔兰时报》（</em> The Irish Times）</a>时谈到人们抱怨艺术家发行长张专辑的人，这让他感到困惑。这是他面对的东西，粉碎了南瓜的“最新专辑” Atum&#39;，该专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-act-1-of-smashing-pumpkins-new-rock-opera-atum-3349537">以三个部分发行，共有33首歌曲</a>。</p><p>科根说，同情泰勒，提到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sinead-oconnor">辛纳德·奥康纳（SinéadO&#39;Connor）</a> ：“既然辛纳德（Sinéad或50  - Sinéad歌曲。那会是一件坏事吗？”</p><p>然后，他向泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）讲话：“泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）是有史以来最有才华的流行艺术家之一。她发行更多音乐是一件坏事？我不能跟随……您可以在Spotify上跳过它。” </p><figure id="attachment_3756255" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3756255" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3756255" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Billy-Corgan-2024.jpg" alt="比利·科根（Billy Corgan" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp